Package com.telenav.kivakit.settings

Class DeploymentSet

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.broadcasters.Multicaster
com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.repeaters.BaseRepeater
com.telenav.kivakit.settings.DeploymentSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Broadcaster, Listener, Repeater, Transceiver, RegistryTrait, Receiver, Transmitter, NamedObject
public class DeploymentSet extends BaseRepeater implements RegistryTrait
A set of Deployment objects, each being a set of settings objects. Deployments can be added to the set from a folder with addDeploymentsIn(Folder). A switch parser to select a deployment from the command line can be retrieved with SwitchParser.deployment(DeploymentSet).
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
See Also:
Deployment, Settings
